Name: Super TECHPACK
About the game: Techpack is back and he's ready to take on a newer, slightly harder challenge. With new and familiar faces to see, the sequel to TECHPACK is bigger, faster, and more difficult than ever. Super TECHPACK is an arcade styled platformer styled after old arcade games from the 1980s. A sequel to the game TECHPACK, this new entry features four playable characters, six persistent enemies, 10 worlds to see, and a lot of charm.
